  <brief_title>Pain Compared Between the First and the Second Surgery in Staged BTKA</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Postoperative Pain in the First and Second Knee in Staged Bilateral Total Knee Arthroplasty: Clinical Evidence That Central Sensitization Increases Systemic Pain Sensitivity</official_title>
