  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      postoperative pain and analgesic consumption between the first and the second surgery would
      be compared in patients undergoing staged bilateral total knee arthroplasty (BTKA).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      postoperative pain and analgesic consumption is compared between the first and second total
      knee arthroplasty (TKA) operation.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
